race.description: Nolans Interstate Tpt Gatton Maiden Plate
race.comment: LINWAR (4) resumed at Doomben with a narrow defeat and then went back and didn't have much luck from a wide gate. Presents fitter again and is still shy of his best. Maps well today and this is grades easier. LONHRO'S SHADOW (8) has switched from a smart Victorian stable on a 37-day return. Missed a whisker as a $2.2 favourite from the speed at Stawell last time after racing keenly through the early and middle stages. Has a handy 2kg claim and has to be kept very safe. BODYSNATCHER (5) resumed at Ipswich and needed the outing. Finally draws a low gate and has been freshened. Fitter and the ability to be in the finish. DUAL MASTERY (6) presents third-up and has the rail. Will be around the mark building on an improved effort.
